{"word":"προκαταλαμβάνω","slug":"προκαταλαμβάνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προκαταλαμβάνω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-λήψομαι</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to seize beforehand, preoccupy</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be preoccupied</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to anticipate, frustrate</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b>:—of persons, <i>to anticipate</i> or <i>surprise</i> them, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><i>to overpower before</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}